        "translations": {
          "en": "He said: Abu al-Hasan Ali ibn Khalid al-Maraghi reported to me. He said: al-Qasim ibn Muhammad al-Dallal narrated to us. He said: Ismail ibn Muhammad al-Muzni narrated to us. He said: Uthman ibn Sa'id narrated to us. He said: Ali ibn Ghurab narrated to us, from Musa ibn Qais al-Hadhrami, from Salama ibn Kuhail, from Ayadh ibn Ayadh, from his father, who said:",
